Test-Harness 3.23

INSTALLATION

To install Test::Harness using ExtUtils::MakeMaker do:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

To use Module::Build (preferred) do:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

This will install Test::Harness and the "prove" program. Type

    prove --help

for more information.

